  "title": "Preschool Cluster Manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Oversee The Operations Of A Cluster Of Three Childcare Centres</li><li>Provide Leadership And Guidance To Centre Principals To Ensure Smooth Centre Operations</li><li>Ensure Compliance With ECDA Licensing SPARK Requirements And Organisational SOPs</li><li>Conduct Regular Centre Visits Audits And Operational Reviews</li><li>Monitor Enrolment Manpower And Centre Performance Against KPIs</li><li>Support Centres Requiring Operational Intervention Or Additional Guidance</li><li>Manage Escalated Feedback From Parents And Stakeholders</li><li>Support New Centre Setup And Organisational Initiatives Where Required</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum Diploma In Early Childhood Care & Education With A Recognised Leadership Qualification</li><li>At Least 5 Years Of Supervisory Or Cluster-Level Experience In Early Childhood</li><li>Proven Ability To Lead Teams Drive Performance And Manage Stakeholders</li></ul>",
