    "description": "<p>About IChild Company<br />\n<br />\nSince 2008, IChild Company Ltd is a Professional EduTalents Consultant firm representing 500 over preschool / educational employers in Singapore, sourcing and advising them on their local / foreign talents needs. <br />\n<br />\nFocus on serving the educational industry, in particularly the Peschool and Pre-Primary sector. we are also an EduTech company, offering a wide range of emerging services to the educational clients so as to serve them holistically and most importantly, knowing their requirements well. The following are some of the services that we provides:<br />\n<br />\n- Info-Tech Solution Services such as the Centre ERP Management System<br />\n- Overseas Business Consultancy<br />\n- Talent Acquisition Consultancy.</p>\n\n<p> </p>\n",
